# Azure Deployment Plan for ConstitutionVerse Project
## **Goal**
Deploy the ConstitutionVerse project to Azure using AZD with Azure Container Apps.

## **Project Information**
**ConstitutionVerse**
- **Stack**: JavaScript (Node.js/React) with Vite build system
- **Type**: Interactive web application about the Indian Constitution
- **Containerization**: Needs to be created
- **Build System**: npm with Vite
- **Port**: 3000
- **Hosting**: Azure Container Apps

## **Azure Resources Architecture**
```mermaid
graph TD
svcazurecontainerapps_constitutionverse["`Name: ConstitutionVerse
Language: js`"]
subgraph "Compute Resources"
subgraph containerappenv["Azure Container Apps (ACA) Environment"]
azurecontainerapps_constitutionverse("`ConstitutionVerse (Azure Container App)`")
end
containerappenv:::cluster
end
svcazurecontainerapps_constitutionverse --> |"hosted on"| azurecontainerapps_constitutionverse
```

- The container app hosts the ConstitutionVerse React application and serves it to users.

